@node The Warrior Window
@chapter The Warrior Window
@cindex The Warrior Window

The Warrior allows you to make Warriors, Technicians, etc. characters.
Warriors are a combination of a character and a mech. There are two 
types of characters. Player character and Non-Player character (NPC).
And several character classes. 
The Mech Warrior is the standard character used for piloting a Mech.
Technicians can not pilot a Mech and gain experience points only by repairing 
Mechs and slavaging Mech parts.
Doctors are used for healing characters.

